{
  "an2.98:0.1": "Numbered Discourses 2.98-117 ",
  "an2.98:0.2": "Chapter on fools",
  "an2.98:1.0": "Fools",
  "an2.98:1.1": "“Monks, these two are fools. ",
  "an2.98:1.2": "Which two? ",
  "an2.98:1.3": "The one who takes up a burden that hasn’t fallen to him, and the one who doesn’t take up a burden that has. ",
  "an2.98:1.4": "These two are fools.”",
